Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还真够年轻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想进攻拉德班・特利亚斯的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须先攻下那个城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦演变为战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必敌我都会出现很多伤亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.44,0:00:30.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个年轻人击败了瓦尔林德骑士团吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城镇究竟会变成怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很想避免战争啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过领主拉德班是一位诚实之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样谈判估计也不会投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过提欧大人的话或许…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.55,0:00:55.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事先准备的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过若对方拒绝投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请说服对方在城外决一胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爱民的拉德班的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会答应的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这个城镇的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.88,0:02:51.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉德班・特利亚斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.85,0:02:58.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是侍奉阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔•康斯坦斯的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说我答应与你谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我已下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要我的爵位和领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就只能用战争奉陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您无论如何都要忠于同盟对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.41,0:03:19.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算终有一日要向马丽娜•克莱榭大人提出效忠请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被这么多人民保护着的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的军队是无法获胜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最主要的是我不想进行伤害人民的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是被人称作英雄的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就请你速速离去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我正有此意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在此之前  我想问一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.52,0:03:46.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你想要的胜利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.48,0:03:53.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合的大军早晚会进攻这个城镇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无非是在此之前苟延残喘而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:04.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯王拉席克也会率领三万人的军队进攻这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,三万…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.08,0:04:07.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望当真正的胜者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我推荐你率领军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从城内出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:21.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 你对同盟的忠诚就保住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,领民也不会受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:29.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能跟英雄提欧•科尔内罗堂堂正正地战到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是得偿所愿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就选择以胜者的身份去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.61,0:04:40.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,使不得 我们决心跟领主大人并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧 各位 没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我死了 这场战斗就能结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.59,0:04:55.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没必要牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉德班大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.14,0:05:06.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们希望今后是您治理这个城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会永远追随你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟联合和同盟都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来保护拉德班大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉德班大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,领主大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您跟我想象中一样 是一名伟大的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 我想请求您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能跟我一起输呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说一起输？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是向同盟效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恳请您珍惜人民的信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是对主君诚实而是对人民诚实吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我理想中的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.62,0:06:07.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须请求大家原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想背叛同盟加入联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要选择与你们共存亡的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的处置就全部交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:34.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 希望你能向我保证 不伤害领民的生命财产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克阁下肯定会隆重接纳您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要离开城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下明明有机会立战功 夺走我的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,战功根本无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟避免了无谓的牺牲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,世间充斥着只对圣印和领地感兴趣的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅爱自己的子民还关心敌人子民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.02,0:07:17.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是走真君主道的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.82,0:07:22.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,掰希望追随您而不是拉席克阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今是追随维拉尔大人之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法答应您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在那一天到来之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能够先保管者我的圣印呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.92,0:07:43.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就将您接纳为从者君主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.72,0:07:44.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:44.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
