Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.85,0:07:53.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.85,0:07:58.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非但投降了  还获得了归顺的保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.76,0:08:31.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克阁下击败了弗维斯王杰里科王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到仅用了短短五天就征讨了弗维斯王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:40.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏如此克劳维斯主动交岀了城池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方未损—兵—卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎阁下与提欧首卞的活跃表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也重创了敌军的士气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人的战功都无与伦比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且实属二人的作风啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前往哈鲁西亚的道路已畅通无阻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家的奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然拒绝了援军的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就有所觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说米尔扎・库切也没用一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就攻下了有力君主的城池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.05,0:09:47.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是达尔塔尼亚大使的子嗣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢我方君主们的情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人很动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想来也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如今失去了塞维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,周边的动向也没有平息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有多余的力量向瓦尔林德派出援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也有批判我的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别看漏君主们的动向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉来错地方了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来错地方了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能一起跳支舞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是阿尔图克伯爵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卢克莱尔伯爵克鲁特•凯拉斯阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得太慢担心死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为路被挡住了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原本想大家一起庆祝英雄到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过有君主并不喜欢阁下的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.17,0:11:08.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾我表妹似乎决心要以武力击败联合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:16.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不给马丽娜留时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,全军进攻同盟领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要攻占了瓦尔林德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能终结同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真有气势啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了道森侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,善于打仗倒是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是通知过你吗 要避免与同盟冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为何不遵从全体意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是全体意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么真希望在发出通知之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也询问下我的意见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:52.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你会遵守君主会议的决定对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不遵守吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.97,0:11:58.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话干万别忘了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.86,0:12:09.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是希望当下的和平能永远持续下去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,自三十年前与同盟决战以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.45,0:12:18.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,化为战场的就只有阿尔图克及周边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:22.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次的会议才是千载难逢的机遇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟如今势头正旺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合想存活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能发起决战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.17,0:12:34.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没法优雅地过下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哈鲁西亚侯爵阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.64,0:12:37.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.80,0:12:37.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:37.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.89,0:12:37.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.93,0:12:37.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.01,0:12:38.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.05,0:12:38.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:38.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,入场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你不远万里地赶来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.42,0:13:11.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是为了见公子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.55,0:13:15.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要横穿大陆我也在所不辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:17.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在大圣堂的时候危险之时救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没能救下两位大公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你就是提欧阁下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到阁下  真是倍感荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想好薛跟你聊一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能这时想候聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望日后让我准备个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜惶恐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是客套话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧 西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现一个得介绍给你们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,自上次君主会议之后就沒见过了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,佩提力克・罗西尼阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  阿尔图克伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这位骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是西斯迪纳出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:21.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说科尔内罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.79,0:14:36.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家名是代代相传的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.55,0:14:39.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的我是平民出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.55,0:14:43.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当上君主之时  取了与故乡有渊源的家名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在西斯迪纳科尔内罗是有来历的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是平民出身的君主能够随便自称的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该改名啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是随便取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.57,0:14:58.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我打算有朝一日要回到故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西斯迪纳是魔境之岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算回来了也没好事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是由我决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够呛的一天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一点没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要喝点茶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文这时候居然没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真罕见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有来客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位非常高的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.86,0:15:44.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  维拉尔大人还在哈鲁西亚公的宫殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人找提欧哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我下过命令  谁都不准进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想跟你们在没有外人的地方聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,倍感光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 在下也有些疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:12.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我等的身份不可与殿下直接谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爵位无非是从父亲那里继承来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说提欧阁下凭自身力量增强圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一时间还当上了塞维斯的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位还到达了子爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我一个人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.03,0:16:28.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有在座的西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及同伴们的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最主要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有维拉尔大人相救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我已经没命了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.38,0:16:38.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说提欧阁下为了西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.09,0:16:43.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不犹豫地舍弃了像这样拼命争取到爵位和领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,引导我这区区流浪之人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这位西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.51,0:16:50.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要牺牲其余的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,得知这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我内心非常震撼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起爵位比起领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,优先选择爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有这样的勇气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.44,0:17:07.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是选择了对我而言最重要的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.70,0:17:13.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言  对马丽娜的爱才是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,得知这份感情无法实现之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至想过自绝性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.59,0:17:25.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  马丽娜开辟了让我们结合的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:26.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今仍爱着马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能跟她在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至愿意抛弃爵位和领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解殿下的感受可这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.61,0:17:43.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜是责任感很强的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.49,0:17:52.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她恐怕想充分履行同盟盟主的责任吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.95,0:17:57.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说马丽娜大人如今仍穿着黑衣仍在服丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟相当了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.75,0:18:07.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望是  整个大陆的君主能不再有纷争齐心合力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后通过谈话选出皇帝就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样纷争便会从大陆消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的时代便能结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我想说的都说完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.94,0:18:29.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我衷心希望你们能幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为了让世人明白一个道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起领地比起爵位还有更重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我向您保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:43.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今在阿尔图克伯爵麾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.92,0:18:47.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在这一主从关系之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.30,0:18:50.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会尽力实现阿莱克希斯殿下的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.76,0:18:54.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有朝一日殿下能与马丽娜大人走到一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.26,0:18:58.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大陆能团结一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.78,0:19:12.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在公开场合之外  希望你能把我当成朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会把你当朋友的
