Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.96,0:19:29.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,屏障啊屏障 万物均不得逾越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮人是什么人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,缄默法则
