Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为狙击手相对各位下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有一名暗影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我被拖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是刺客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,击败对方了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.61,0:21:09.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:17.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我害得你们陷入了危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很愧疚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.17,0:21:37.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是找错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀公爵未遂的罪也绝对不轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果得知把阿莱克希斯大人也卷进来了
